rows.label: qev086705_MSG0001
rows.name:
My name's Nastasha, of the Reclaimers.
It's an honor to meet you guys.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086705_MSG0002
rows.name: Wait. You know who we are?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086705_MSG0003
rows.name: Doesn't everyone?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086705_MSG0004
rows.name:
You guys clear all the most dangerous missions.
You're BLADE superstars![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086705_MSG0005
rows.name: My team has some serious Lin Lee Koo fans.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086705_MSG0006
rows.name: What?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086705_MSG0007
rows.name: You think we could...maybe get an autograph later?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086705_MSG0008
rows.name: Um...okay?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086705_MSG0009
rows.name: Who on team Nastasha is biggest Tatsu fan?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086705_MSG0010
rows.name: Who ISN'T a fan of the bravest little Nopon on Mira?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086705_MSG0011
rows.name: This...single greatest moment of Tatsu's life...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086705_MSG0012
rows.name:
When we left Earth, it felt like the end.
Like everything was over.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086705_MSG0013
rows.name:
But life moves on, and people with it—
no matter where they end up.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086705_JNK0010
rows.name: Grin

rows.label: qev086705_SEL0011
rows.name: Say you can imagine worse places to start over.

rows.label: qev086705_JNK0020
rows.name: Assert

rows.label: qev086705_SEL0021
rows.name: Say you won't just move on—you'll prosper.

rows.label: qev086705_MSG0014
rows.name: And I'll be damned if we ever lose this one.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086705_MSG0015
rows.name:
We'll fight to protect Mira,
for ourselves and everyone else on it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086705_MSG0016
rows.name: You really think that's possible on a planet like this?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086705_MSG0017
rows.name:
No, we just have to MAKE it possible.
It's up to us.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086705_MSG0018
rows.name: And not just up to humans.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086705_MSG0019
rows.name: Nopon and others must all work to prosper together![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086705_MSG0020
rows.name: Yeah...that's right.[ST:wait ]
